  <chapter>
    <!-- DNT-Start --><title>Next Steps</title><!-- DNT-End -->

    <para>To familiarize yourself with the Eclipse <!-- DNT-Start -->IDE<!-- DNT-End --> and the <!-- DNT-Start -->ECL<!-- DNT-End --> Development
    perspective, we recommend working the following tutorials in Eclipse:
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem>
          <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->HPCC<!-- DNT-End --> Data Tutorial</emphasis></para>
        </listitem>

